MAGNETIC_DEVICE_REMOVED: 'đź§˛',
DEVICE_OFFLINE: 'đź“´',
```

---

#### [MODIFY] [api.js](file:///c:/Users/Dhanush/internship-project2/client/src/api.js)

Add `reportTamperEvent(data)` function that calls `POST /api/alerts/tamper`.

